Description: Distributed task orchestrator CLI for TaskFlow
 TaskFlow CLI is a command-line interface for managing distributed tasks
 in the TaskFlow orchestration system. It provides an interactive terminal
 interface for creating, managing, and monitoring tasks.
 .
 Features:
  - Interactive CLI with command history
  - Task creation and management
  - File upload capabilities
  - Real-time task monitoring
  - User authentication and authorization
